task.summary: Switchong ACRA crash reporter from Iriscouch to Cloudant

New feature - add Activity showing GPS status, Satellites charateristics and lication data in real time - the notification show the saved point total number - the calculation of used satellites is done with SNR (>0). So if a satellite has SNR >0 then is considered used
Bug fix and optimization - Use Locale.ITALY in string convertion - Use listview to display the saved point file (increase performance)

New feature - add Activity showing GPS status, Satellites charateristics and lication data in real time - the notification show the saved point total number - the calculation of used satellites is done with SNR (>0). So if a satellite has SNR >0 then is considered used
Bug fix and optimization - Use Locale.ITALY in string convertion - Use listview to display the saved point file (increase performance) - The lock screen notification now display information on service status

New project organization - build split in main, staging and production flavors - Added a changelog file for future credits display New feature - Fragments to display various information and behaviour - Augmented reality to show satellites - Kalman filter and post rotation averages Bug fix and optimization - Updated the ACRA library - Scratch of a new main service and interface (future rationalization of sensor and GPS listeners)
